WEBVTT

00:00:03.539 --> 00:00:06.615
Znate, budimo se svakog jutra,

00:00:06.615 --> 00:00:09.135
obučete se, obujete,

00:00:09.135 --> 00:00:11.647
krenete među svet.

00:00:11.647 --> 00:00:15.898
Nameravate da se vratite, svučete,

00:00:15.898 --> 00:00:18.123
odete u krevet,

00:00:18.123 --> 00:00:19.877
budite se, opet sve iznova,

00:00:19.877 --> 00:00:23.025
i to očekivanje, taj ritam

00:00:23.025 --> 00:00:25.295
nam pomažu da imamo strukturu

00:00:25.295 --> 00:00:28.883
da organizujemo sebe i sopstvene živote

00:00:28.883 --> 00:00:32.363
i unesemo dozu predvidljivosti.